            "id": 6011136,
            "title": "〈熱門股〉光聖受惠美系大廠需求強勁  日線連拉3根紅K創波段高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光通訊廠光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>)，今年持續受惠美系大廠需求強勁，讓公司延續去年的需求動能持穩成長，加上光聖近期已標到馬國 (Data center) 大單，預計第 3 季開始出貨，激勵本周股價連收 3 日紅 K，周漲 3.78%，收 480.5 元，股價創波段新高。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011136%2Fl%2Fa6329fb0390055fe82a196b1b309d94a.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈熱門股〉光聖受惠美系大廠需求強勁  日線連拉3根紅K創波段高。(鉅亨網記者黃皓宸攝)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光聖高層表示，公司不受關稅影響而放緩成長，美國基礎建設持續布建，加速光聖美系大客戶數據中心相關被動產品拉貨需求，目前美系客戶訂單已看到年底，預期全年被動產品年增 15%-20%，主動產品線年增 20%，全年業績增長可望達到年增 10-15%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光聖本周一掃上周陰霾，連收 3 日紅 K，股價最高衝到 495 元，進逼 500 元大關，創波段新高，量增價揚，周成交量超過 2 萬張，較前一周增近 9 倍以上，股價也向上攻破短期均線，站上年線大關。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光聖表示，面對全球關稅貿易戰，未來將持續維持與美系客戶間的商談溝通，朝不影響雙方獲利的目標努力，匯率也透過自然避險與金融避險工具，降低匯率評價損失。隨著 AI 與雲端應用的快速發展，公司的營運表現持續加溫中。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>光聖<span style=\"color:#000000\"> 4 月合併</span><a href=\"https://udn.com/search/tagging/2/%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6\"><span style=\"color:#000000\">營收</span></a><span style=\"color:#000000\">為 10.57 億元</span>，因應美國本土 AI 基礎建設布建需求升溫，帶動營收月增 83.35%、年增 194.59%，重返 10 億元大關，單月營收創歷史次高。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img data-cnyeschart=\"cnyeschart\" src=\"https://so.cnyes.com/mobilechart/MobileChart.aspx?markettype=twstock&amp;charttype1=kchart&amp;stockcode=6442&amp;imgwidth=580&amp;imgheight=500&amp;bgcolor=2\"/>\n<figcaption> </figcaption>\n</figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
